**/.DS_Store

# Generated by deploy — root-level symlink to AGENTS.md (source of truth).
/CLAUDE.md

# Machine-specific SSH config (real hostnames/IPs, usernames) — lives at
# $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/ssh/config.local in practice, outside this repo
# entirely, so this never actually matches anything; here only as a
# safety net in case it's ever created inside the repo by mistake.
ssh/config.local

# Scoped-down GH_TOKEN for .envrc — never commit a real token
.envrc.local

# Machine-private Claude Code layer files — internal/work platform tooling that
# must never reach this public repo. Kept on-machine; the whole claude/rules/
# tree deploys as one symlink, so any file physically present here (tracked or
# not) reaches $CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR/rules and Claude Code auto-discovers it — no
# wiring needed. A fresh clone simply lacks these files, so nothing appears.
# See claude/README.md § Private layer files.
claude/rules/layer2-platform/local.md
claude/rules/layer2-platform/bytecloud.md
